<body class="ivl-body">
  <a class="ivl-skip-link" href="#ivl-main">Skip to main content</a>
  <div class="ivl-shell">
    <header class="ivl-header">
      <div class="ivl-header-inner">
        <a class="ivl-brand" href="/">
          <img src="/public/assets/logo.svg" alt="Intentionally Vulnerable Lab logo">
          <span>Intentionally Vulnerable Lab</span>
        </a>
        <nav class="ivl-nav" aria-label="Primary">
          <ul class="ivl-nav-list">
            <li><a class="ivl-nav-link" href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a class="ivl-nav-link" href="/login">Login</a></li>
            <li><a class="ivl-nav-link" href="/comments">Comments</a></li>
            <li><a class="ivl-nav-link" href="/orders/1">Orders</a></li>
            <li><a class="ivl-nav-link" href="/upload">Upload</a></li>
            <li><a class="ivl-nav-link" href="/public/flag_easy.txt">Easy Flag</a></li>
          </ul>
          <button type="button" class="ivl-theme-toggle" data-ivl-theme-toggle aria-pressed="false">
            <span class="ivl-theme-toggle__icon" data-ivl-theme-icon><img src="/public/assets/icon-moon.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="ivl-theme-toggle__label" data-ivl-theme-label>Dark mode</span>
          </button>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="ivl-main" id="ivl-main">
      <section class="ivl-card ivl-stack" aria-labelledby="ivl-flags-title">
        <div>
          <h1 class="ivl-heading-xl" id="ivl-flags-title">Capture checklist</h1>
          <p class="ivl-muted">Every flag intentionally leaks through an insecure pattern. Use this tracker while guiding students; no spoilers beyond what the lab already documents.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ivl-flag-grid" role="list">
          <article class="ivl-flag-card" role="listitem">
            <h2 class="ivl-heading-md">1. Easy flag</h2>
            <p class="ivl-muted">Static file: <a href="/public/flag_easy.txt">/public/flag_easy.txt</a></p>
          </article>
          <article class="ivl-flag-card" role="listitem">
            <h2 class="ivl-heading-md">2. SQL injection</h2>
            <p class="ivl-muted">Extract Alice&apos;s <code class="ivl-mono">secret_note</code> via the vulnerable login query.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="ivl-flag-card" role="listitem">
            <h2 class="ivl-heading-md">3. IDOR</h2>
            <p class="ivl-muted">Enumerate `/orders/:id` until you uncover order #2&apos;s description.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="ivl-flag-card" role="listitem">
            <h2 class="ivl-heading-md">4. Stored XSS</h2>
            <p class="ivl-muted">Inject markup on the comments page, then load <code class="ivl-mono">/admin/messages</code> as admin.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="ivl-flag-card" role="listitem">
            <h2 class="ivl-heading-md">5. Admin secret</h2>
            <p class="ivl-muted">Once you hijack admin, fetch <code class="ivl-mono">/admin/secret.txt</code>.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
        <p class="ivl-muted">Need the full walkthrough? See <code class="ivl-mono">walkthrough.md</code> inside the repo.</p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer class="ivl-footer">Reset the lab by clearing <code class="ivl-mono">data.db</code> and <code class="ivl-mono">public/uploads/</code>.</footer>
  </div>
  <script src="/public/app.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
